Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:34.87,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:41.92,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:46.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:55.46,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:02.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:06.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:10.55,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:13.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:18.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:21.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:28.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:32.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:36.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:46.49,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:51.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:34.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:41.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}随心所欲地去描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:46.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描绘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:55.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}万里无云的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无边无际的蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:02.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}纯洁无瑕的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:06.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈着无限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:10.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终于能自由翱翔于天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:13.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}长出了美丽的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:18.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无瑕的瞳孔在寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:21.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那无数的愿望中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:28.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一个能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:32.08,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不愿让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:36.08,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要紧紧抓住那梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:46.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描写
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:51.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈愿的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1000,8)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}初阵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:42.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:49.06,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:57.72,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:05.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:14.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:22.28,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:30.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:38.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:46.27,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:54.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:42.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:49.06,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤独中寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:57.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用灵魂连结我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:05.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用爱恋温暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:14.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那颤抖的祈愿之声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:22.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:30.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不断交替的轮回之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:38.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不终结的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:46.27,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不断轮回的 那些传颂之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:54.41,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守护着安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帮厚颜无耻的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟趁火打劫地硬闯入我们的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通道的尽头已经准备好了船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来还有些要事没办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡托玛乌 带着迪利霍莱先走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行 我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来的话 连拖延时间也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 这孩子就托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人 你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利 要变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和姐姐大人在一起的话我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成为比谁都强壮…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…比谁都高大的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 没有发现我们的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱殿下 轻敌会招致死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有轻敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个女人 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪 怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深入追敌危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手好像有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方也有伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敌方大部队到来之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且算是完成了部分地区的解放
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 讨论今后的方针
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说 当然是维持现在这种战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下也赞成 现在势头正在我方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有忘记什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都已经很劳累了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把本不是士兵的他们带上战场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把伤员以及妇女儿童转移到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才能毫无顾虑地去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道潜入那座城堡的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座城堡要从地下的湖中汲取大量的水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿着那里的水路就可以潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你为什么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为剑奴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于捷径小道当然是知道的很详细了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这些话可信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这些事情的判断 不正是首领的职责吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这场战役中 取下敌方统领的首级
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为水路狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有少数人可以潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样如果能通往敌军正中央的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能通往敌军正中央的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拼了命也要把他们的王…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果迪利霍莱大人有什么不测的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由谁来继续率领卡露拉阿滋雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不想错失这次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 就由我们来担任诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面牵制敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘着这个机会 请想办法潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替同伴着想的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战役 无论如何一定要获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得这场战役的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家所期盼的 自由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把卡露拉让给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么我都可以给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一片赤诚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 卡露拉她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是能像东西一样转让的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 为什么要提这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能那样痛扁我的人 那个女人还是头一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有些地方和我已经失散了的姐姐大人有点像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然又像完全相反的两个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人温柔 贤淑 可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的理想和憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比姐姐大人更好的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止从没有见过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒真是截然相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的战役结束以后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到图斯克尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 只要有当天充饥的粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并能以虫鸣为安眠曲 以大地为枕席
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就这样丢弃了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前和我说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己没有过去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这样的我说过 我还是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才能坚持活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 过去也不是想丢弃就能够丢弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在迪利霍莱大人回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要想办法坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗 我有事问你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位女性拜托我助你一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡托玛乌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是王的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说用活人当苗床的话才能开出最美的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些…全部都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯欧卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些可是为了你而倾注着感情培养的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱 现在先专念于战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉 之后再问你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们同胞的自由 打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好有朝气的孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 明明就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于回到我的身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 这并不代表我的回归
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑奴的叛乱什么的从一开始我就没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找到你 我还造了这座花圃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:14:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉 不 卡露拉阿滋雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉阿滋雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就是为了要引我出来才策划的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是卡露拉阿滋雷 真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你高兴我可是别出心裁地做了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 你所喜爱的故乡 拉鲁玛尼奥努之花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回到我的身边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和作为公主时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我会提供给你更为奢侈的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在王宫的生活 除了烦闷就是无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 您就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 就不得不硬让你回到我身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:14:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别离开我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个单细胞的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只会一味猛冲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说我也会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利 你是个没用的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你已经为了大家站起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你也和以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能再回到我的身边的这个瞬间让我感到多么的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同胞一直以来承受的痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉阿滋雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别侮辱这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是姐姐大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多么想再次见到您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像把我和谁搞错了 你认错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 您在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面众多的同胞正在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那些同胞 你还有要做的事不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话要说的话 在那之后也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请答应我 哪里都不要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 但不是说等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有说过这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样 都约定了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是这样的话太悲哀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:18:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉是笨蛋…大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…有时自己也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉利亚基纳族人迪利霍莱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经拿下仇敌斯欧卡斯的首级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告卡露拉阿滋雷的独立
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来之后 就再没有离开过小柚身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡也要跟着来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有和哥哥一起洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 我没这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢 打算让我等到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来道谢的 这样的话请不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然自称是王了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该和其他的王平起平坐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破这些规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能称作是王了 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和以前一样朝气蓬勃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…图斯克尔的王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和您是初次见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我的名字是迪利霍莱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了贵国支援我国物资的事 特此前来道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来准备对你们见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有个女人向我请求援助你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位现在精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 太过于精神了 让我很为难
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱大人 有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去的话 还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们一起走也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况他是你唯一的亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人你看来搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的只是一个叫做卡露拉的只属于主人的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了


